Package org.bson.io

Interface BsonInput

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ByteBufferBsonInput
    public interface BsonInput
extends Closeable
    An input stream that is optimized for reading BSON values directly from the underlying stream.
    Since:
    3.0
